---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="もっと充実したテニスライフを実現">
  <!-- Hero with background image -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[600px] flex items-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src={`${base}images/hero/court.jpg`} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-dark/90 to-primary/80"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center text-white">
      <img src={`${base}images/logo/logo.png`} alt="御忍庭球塾" class="h-20 md:h-28 mx-auto mb-8" />
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight drop-shadow-lg">
        御忍庭球塾
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl font-medium text-white/90 mb-4">
        もっと充実したテニスライフを実現
      </p>
      <p class="text-white/70 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        札幌市白石区を拠点に、少人数制レッスンで<br class="hidden md:inline" />
        一人ひとりの上達をサポートします
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href={`${base}courses`} class="bg-accent hover:bg-accent-light text-primary-dark font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition shadow-lg text-lg">
          コース・料金を見る
        </a>
        <a href="https://lin.ee/2CKErIS" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="border-2 border-white/80 hover:bg-white/10 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition text-lg">
          LINE でお問い合わせ
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Overview -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-bg">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4">御忍庭球塾の特徴</h2>
      <p class="text-text-light text-center mb-14 max-w-2xl mx-auto">本気で上達したい方のためのテニススクールです</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition group">
          <div class="h-48 bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <img src={`${base}images/features/lesson-snapshot.png`} alt="少人数レッスン" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">少人数制（最大6名）</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
              1レッスン最大6名まで。コーチの目が一人ひとりに行き届く環境で、確実に上達できます。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition group">
          <div class="h-48 bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <img src={`${base}images/hero/court.jpg`} alt="デコターフコート" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">デコターフコート</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
              PLACE OF SPORTS NEO のインドアデコターフコートを使用。天候に左右されない快適な環境です。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition group">
          <div class="h-48 bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <img src={`${base}images/features/lesson-snapshot.png`} alt="動画で振り返り" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition duration-500" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">動画で振り返り</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light leading-relaxed">
              レッスンを動画で撮影。自分のプレーを客観的に確認し、効率的にスキルアップできます。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-10">
        <a href={`${base}features`} class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary-light text-white font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition">
          詳しく見る →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OSHINOBI GUT 24 Banner -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-primary-dark text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iNDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNDAiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PGNpcmNsZSBjeD0iMjAiIGN5PSIyMCIgcj0iMiIgZmlsbD0id2hpdGUiLz48L3N2Zz4=')] bg-repeat"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10">
        <div class="md:w-1/3 flex justify-center">
          <img src={`${base}images/logo/gut24-logo.png`} alt="OSHINOBI GUT 24" class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl" />
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-2/3 text-center md:text-left">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4">OSHINOBI GUT 24</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-2">24時間受付のガット張替サービス</p>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-8 text-lg">JR白石駅北口 徒歩2分 ・ 全品工賃込み ・ 2,800円〜</p>
          <a href={`${base}gut24`} class="bg-accent hover:bg-accent-light text-primary-dark font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition inline-block text-lg shadow-lg">
            詳しく見る
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- YouTube -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-bg">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">ダブルスの技術を毎週配信中</h2>
        <p class="text-text-light">YouTubeチャンネルで毎週日曜日にテニス技術動画を投稿しています</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <iframe
          class="w-full h-full"
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bXEScAkbFYI"
          title="テニス解説動画"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKtgQuL9B0c8y42hHnx8JQQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-primary font-bold hover:underline text-lg">
          YouTubeチャンネルを見る →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src={`${base}images/hero/court.jpg`} alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary-dark/85"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center text-white">
      <img src={`${base}images/logo/mascot.png`} alt="マスコット" class="h-24 mx-auto mb-6" />
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">体験レッスン受付中</h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 mb-8 text-lg">
        一般月曜コース・一般木曜コースは体験受講が可能です。<br />
        初回 3,000円でお試しいただけます。
      </p>
      <a href="https://lin.ee/2CKErIS" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="bg-accent hover:bg-accent-light text-primary-dark font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-lg transition inline-block text-lg shadow-lg">
        LINE で体験を申し込む
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
